title: ardent censor
body: i was having a game with a mate doing botlane. i was support and i built a ardent censor and for some reason it was decreasing my adcs attack speed from 1.56 to 1.53 il keep and eye out for it again but it should be increasing atk spd not decreasing

replies.body: Theres plenty of things that could have happened, for example: Fervor's stacks wearing off
